node.text:
Spotting sea snakes with @brodiemoss 😱 Apply for a feature following the link in our bio and we will publish your photos in our account: @nomadfervor

“Sea snakes normally avoid humans but this time of year they become very active, sexually frustrated and potentially aggressive as they search for a mate 🐍 like this old fella who appeared from the ocean floor and followed me around on my paddle board before disappearing 😅”

What would you do in this situation? 😱

📽 @brodiemoss
📍Australia

node.text:
Discovering underwater history in Norway, Aqaba, Egypt and Malta. Tag someone who needs to see this! 🤯 Wanna see your pictures posted in our account? Apply for a feature on nomadfervor.com (link in my bio: @nomadfervor) 

Locations:
1. S/S Frankenwald near Gulen, Norway
2, 5, 6, 7, 9, 10. Aqaba, Jordan
3. The P31 from Comino in Malta
4. The Giannis D at Abu Nuhas, Red Sea, Egypt
8. Rozi the tug boat in Ċirkewwa near the ferry terminal to Gozo, Malta.

📷 @alex_dawson_photography
